真正掌握介词，不只是选出答案，还要说明句子把参照项构形成了什么。部分题目在不同语境下允许多个答案；括号给出的语境用来指定本题希望表达的构形。答案区给出该语境下的优选答案，并说明重要替代形式。建议先独立完成，再查看答案。

== 一、同一场景，不同构形

为每组句子选择合适介词，并用“地点锚点、内部、表面、路径、目标”等词解释。

+ The students are #blank school.（他们在校上课）
+ Two technicians are working #blank the school.（他们正在校舍内部维修）
+ A flag is flying #blank the school roof.
+ Someone is waiting #blank the door.
+ There is a small window #blank the door.
+ A child is standing #blank the doorway.

== 二、位置与参照系

+ The village lies #blank the mountains.（群山之中）
+ The temperature fell #blank zero.
+ A lamp hangs #blank the table.（只说明高度较高，不突出覆盖或跨越）
+ The keys are #blank the newspaper.（被报纸盖住）
+ Negotiations took place #blank the five countries.（五国被分别识别并建立协商关系）
+ She felt relaxed #blank friends.（把朋友看成围绕她的群体环境）
+ The new car park is #blank the east of the station.（位于车站以东）
+ The café is #blank the northern edge of the square.

== 三、位置、路径与目标

在 #en[in / into / through / across / along / to / towards] 中选择，并说明介词短语承担什么路径角色。

+ He walked #blank the room for ten minutes.
+ He then walked #blank the next room.
+ The train passed #blank a long tunnel.
+ They swam #blank the river from one bank to the other.
+ A footpath runs #blank the coast.（沿海岸线延伸）
+ She turned #blank the sound.
+ We drove #blank the station and parked outside.
+ The road runs #blank the village, following a route inside the built-up area.

== 四、时间关系

+ The seminar starts #blank 9:30 #blank Monday morning.
+ I completed the report #blank two hours.（从开始到完成共用时两小时）
+ Please reply #blank two hours; an earlier reply is welcome.
+ The lights went out #blank the meeting.
+ The meeting continued #blank three hours.
+ She has visited us twice #blank January.
+ The parcel will arrive #blank 2 and 4 pm.
+ The office is open #blank 9 #blank 5.
+ We did not leave #blank midnight.
+ #blank 2020, the company was already operating in Asia.

== 五、补语形式与词类

判断高亮词是介词、小品词，还是不定式标记。

+ She looked #hl[after] the child.
+ She turned the television #hl[off].
+ I look forward #hl[to] meeting you.
+ I hope #hl[to] meet you.
+ What are you talking #hl[about]?
+ He looked #hl[up to] his teacher.（分别判断 up 和 to）

然后改正错误：

+ between you and I
+ despite of the rain
+ because of it was raining
+ look forward to meet you
+ involve in community projects

== 六、抽象关系与搭配

+ a rise #blank 12% / a rise #blank prices
+ an impact #blank public health
+ pay #blank credit card / cut it #blank a knife
+ a solution #blank the problem
+ interested #blank learning languages
+ a gift #blank my sister
+ tremble #blank fear
+ The bridge was designed #blank a local engineer.

== 七、IELTS 句子修订

判断关系或比较对象是否清楚，并重写句子。若原句在特定语境下可以成立，请说明成立条件。

+ Compared with 2020, the city was higher.
+ In contrast to last year, sales increased.
+ On behalf of future generations, governments should reduce emissions.
+ The factory is behind the housing area.（这是一张没有观察方向的地图）
+ The liquid moves along the pipe into the tank.（改写为明确突出管道内部通道的版本）

== 八、一景多说

每题写出两个都正确的版本，并说明介词变化怎样改变构形。

+ 用 #en[through] 和 #en[across] 分别描述“走过同一座公园”。
+ 用 #en[between] 和 #en[among] 分别描述“五国进行协商”。
+ 用 #en[above] 和 #en[over] 分别描述“一盏灯位于桌子上方”。
+ 用 #en[at] 和 #en[in] 分别描述“学生在学校”。

